his life.

02:52.300 --> 02:56.266
♪ ♪

02:56.300 --> 02:57.400
- All right,
let's just get--

02:57.433 --> 02:59.633
get these fenders
up for now.

02:59.667 --> 03:01.233
- (BLEEP) sakes.

03:01.266 --> 03:03.233
- We're proceeding out.

03:03.266 --> 03:04.700
Jesus.

03:04.734 --> 03:06.700
- Ashton, how are you
doing, bud?

03:06.734 --> 03:08.200
You okay?

03:12.433 --> 03:15.300
- Okay, start pulling
that line up on board.

03:18.300 --> 03:19.600
- Ross, Ross.
Lee.

03:19.633 --> 03:20.633
- Yeah, go ahead.

