and ready for you.

09:56.200 --> 09:58.000
- Oh, yeah, when you're ready,
you can start.

09:58.033 --> 09:59.133
Push the green button
and you'll away.

09:59.166 --> 10:01.000
[motor revving]

10:01.033 --> 10:08.000
♪ ♪

