37:47.300 --> 37:49.734
- We are going to have
a meeting shortly,

37:49.767 --> 37:52.066
and I'll tell you right now,

37:52.100 --> 37:53.667
it's gonna be a very
sobering meeting.

37:53.700 --> 37:58.567
♪ ♪

38:02.533 --> 38:05.066
